t":"They tend to have more widespread symptoms and aren't as sharply localized as this seems to be.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.035264,0.043456,0.049739,0.057313,0.066258,0.076902,0.08932,0.099771,0.11276,0.12817,0.13662,0.10443],"unified_progress":[0.040235,0.05568,0.065869,0.073523,0.083301,0.092046,0.094892,0.10023,0.10234,0.10437,0.10071,0.086807]},{"section":18,"text":"So, putting all this together, the sudden, sharp nature of the pain, its location, and the triggers make trigeminal neuralgia seem like the most likely explanation.","dimension":3,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.018217,0.031419,0.039601,0.047205,0.054307,0.062071,0.070993,0.078312,0.091661,0.11657,0.17823,0.21141],"unified_progress":[0.021965,0.036453,0.046232,0.055659,0.063652,0.077378,0.081795,0.094112,0.10444,0.11215,0.13783,0.16834]},{"section":19,"text":"Yeah, I'm leaning towards that.","dimension":3,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.012578,0.023988,0.029541,0.03542,0.040582,0.046458,0.053031,0.058421,0.071514,0.10114,0.20989,0.31744],"unified_progress":[0.010211,0.019999,0.026829,0.034441,0.041022,0.056634,0.061681,0.083537,0.10142,0.11707,0.17522,0.27193]},{"section":20,"text":"It fits with everything she's describing.","dimension":3,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.017465,0.026879,0.030967,0.035893,0.04083,0.046781,0.053867,0.060385,0.074746,0.10598,0.20606,0.30015],"unified_progress":[0.013534,0.022079,0.027639,0.034152,0.040919,0.052976,0.059214,0.079046,0.096933,0.11725,0.17486,0.28139]},{"section":21,"text":"So, I'd say the most likely diagnosis here is trigeminal neuralgia.","dimension":3,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.011703,0.019364,0.023742,0.028893,0.033669,0.039422,0.046063,0.052071,0.065838,0.10004,0.22583,0.35337],"unified_progress":[0.0076908,0.014397,0.019355,0.025603,0.031805,0.044205,0.051213,0.072121,0.092574,0.11705,0.19012,0.33387]}],"qwq-32b":[{"section"